{"tid":2320813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9吹民眾支持率超90%　支那官員轟美國「有什麼資格談人權」","createTime":"2020-12-11T05:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T08:14:07.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"407d95500e5ee21ebda54c210114b4c487356dcb","tid":2320813,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"《世界人權宣言》發表72週年，中國常駐聯合國日內瓦代表團發言人劉玉印11日針對「世<br />\n界人權日」發表談話。他指出，「中國共產黨和中國政府享有的民眾支持率高達90%以上<br />\n，我們為此深感自豪。」他還引述報告，有87%的美國人對國家現狀不滿，反問，「這樣<br />\n的政府有什麼資格談人權？」<br />\n <br />\n《中新社》報導，劉玉印在聲明中首天提到，《世界人權宣言》是人類歷史上具有重大意<br />\n義的文獻，對世界人權事業發展產生了深刻影響。72年來，國際人權事業取得巨大進展，<br />\n同時仍然面臨巨大挑戰。實現人人得享人權的崇高目標，需要國際社會的共同努力，尤其<br />\n要避免人權被政治化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201211/1874128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201211%2F1874128.htm&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=4877ec62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201211/1874128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"260db329f0cc236284ce5ef9c976181e1c2623e1","tid":2320813,"uid":72304,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"正正因為佢地可以不滿政府, 先顯得人地有人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd33aecc063e4fb642d33bab01190aeb70a0af5","tid":2320813,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:47:00.000Z","msg":"中國式民主 中國式人權<br />\n贏到開巷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe7100e5c7f0cab2d0d47a6db6df9266334bc29","tid":2320813,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"事實係中國14億入面大部份都支持共產黨<br />\n你吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"22608144b40428a31046f91c64ff512f62e3d8f0","tid":2320813,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"